# Core Project Rules
- **Framework**: Next.js 15+ (App Router), Tailwind CSS, TypeScript.
- **Suppression**: Always maintain 'suppressHydrationWarning' on the <html> tag in the root layout.
- **Behavior**: Be concise. No prose.
- **Zero Placeholder Policy**: Fully implement functions; no // TODOs.
- **Server-First**: Use React Server Components by default.
